    "@type": "MLModel",
    "name": "ParTrans-X",
    "description": "ParTrans-X is proposed as an efficient parallel framework for translating embedding methods, designed to overcome the major limitation of these state-of-the-art methods—their time-consuming training process. The framework enables the methods to be paralleled without locks by utilizing the distinguished structures of knowledge graphs. Experiments validating ParTrans-X on two datasets using three typical translating embedding methods (TransE, TransH, and a more efficient variant) demonstrated that it can speed up the training process by more than an order of magnitude.",
